<main id="content" class="content"> <header> <h1 class="title">Prayer of St. Thomas</h1>
 <p class="subtitle" role="doc-subtitle">Nov 12, 2016 00:00</p>
</header> <blockquote class="bigquote">
 <p>
Grant me, O Lord my God, <br></br>
a mind to know you, <br></br>
a heart to seek you, <br></br>
conduct pleasing to you, <br></br>
faithful perseverance in waiting for you, <br></br>
and a hope of finally embracing you.
</p>
</blockquote>

 <p class="bigquote">
St. Thomas Aquinas
</p>


